<p style="text-indent: 0;">Dr Sir</p>
<p>Please to receive and pay the above Accts agreeably to the Memm furnishd you by Yr Most Obedt</p>
<div class="closer">
<p class="signed">Go: Washington<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0002-fn-0017" id="GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0002-fn-0017-ptr">17</a></p>
