<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Autograph Document: a document in the handwriting of the author ]">AD</abbr>, <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Huntington Library, Art Collections and Botanical Gardens, San Marino, Calif. ]">CSmH</span>.
 The document at <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Huntington Library, Art Collections and Botanical Gardens, San Marino, Calif. ]">CSmH</span> is not as complete but provides some additional information.</p>

