<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0002-fn-0007-ptr" id="GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0002-fn-0007">7</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-10-02-0274-0001" class="document">Memorandum to Fielding Lewis, 30 April</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-10-02-0274-0001&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0001-fn-0006#GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0001-fn-0006" class="document">reference in note 6</a><span class="choice deletion" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover_choice ] header=[]  body=[ Deleted: ', printed above' &lt;span style='font-size: 90%'&gt;[[2014-11-25]]&lt;/span&gt; ]"><img alt="deletion" src="images/deletion_mark-trans.png" style="border:none;vertical-align: text-bottom; padding-right:2px"/></span>. The copy at <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Huntington Library, Art Collections and Botanical Gardens, San Marino, Calif. ]">CSmH</span> gives the amount as 525.8.0.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0002-fn-0008-ptr" id="GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0002-fn-0008">8</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-10-02-0274-0001" class="document">Memorandum to Fielding Lewis, 30 April</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-10-02-0274-0001&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0001-fn-0004#GEWN-02-10-02-0274-0001-fn-0004" class="document">reference in note 4</a><span class="choice deletion" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover_choice ] header=[]  body=[ Deleted: ', printed above' &lt;span style='font-size: 90%'&gt;[[2014-11-25]]&lt;/span&gt; ]"><img alt="deletion" src="images/deletion_mark-trans.png" style="border:none;vertical-align: text-bottom; padding-right:2px"/></span>.</p>

</div>
