   <p>The copy at <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Huntington Library, Art Collections and Botanical Gardens, San Marino, Calif. ]">CSmH</span> has Mr Jas Mill.</p>

